title: HOUR 3- The Lakers Are Who We Thought They Were & Ryan Hollins - Sep 07, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 3- The Lakers Are Who We Thought They Were & Ryan Hollins - Sep 07, 2020
description:
FOX Sports Radio hosts Jason Smith and Rob Parker are in for Dan and the Danettes, and the guys explain why the Los Angeles Lakers will only go as far as LeBron James and Anthony Davis can carry them, and what we can realistically expect from Cam Newton in his first year with the New England Patriots. Plus, former NBA veteran Ryan Hollins swings by to explain why Giannis Antetokounmpo is overrated, why closeout games are so hard to win in the NBA Playoffs, and much more!
